			Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idMerchantClone, false, true)
	
			Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idCamelClone05, marker_CamelEnd, "NPC_Walk", false)

			Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idMerchantClone, 0.3)
	
		end
